---
import InquiryFormGeneralContact from "@/components/inquiry/InquiryFormGeneralContact.astro";
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
import "animate.css";
---

<ContentLayout
  title="Careers at With the Ranks"
  bannerCategory="Careers"
  bannerTitle="Come work with us."
  bannerSubtitle="If you're passionate about building tech for good causes, we want to talk to you!"
  theme="light"
  flushMainBottom={true}
  toc={[
	{ id: "about-our-work", label: "About our work" },
	{ id: "contact", label: "Connect with us" },
  ]}
>
  <div class="mx-auto min-w-0 max-w-full break-words" id="about-our-work">
    <p>
      Whether you're a designer, developer, project manager, or just interested
      in helping good causes figure out tech, we're always looking to connect
      with good people.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our work spans the gamut from the tiniest city council campaigns to large
      global nonprofits and national political campaigns, and we're also
      building some exciting internal products and services, too.
    </p>

    <p>
      We love to build and host high-performing websites and apps, develop
      cohesive tech strategies to organize at scale, run A/B tests to optimize
      websites, improve accessibility and page speed on existing websites, run
      peer-to-peer texting campaigns through our self hosted fork of Spoke,
      build and maintain open source tech tools, and a whole lot more.
    </p>

    <p>
      If that sounds like something you're interested in and you think you can contribute to our cooperative, let us know via the
      form below and we'll be in touch!
    </p>
    <div
      id="contact"
      class="relative z-0 mt-12 min-w-0 w-screen max-w-none border-t border-black/20 bg-brand-blue px-4 py-12 ml-[calc(50%-50vw)] mr-[calc(50%-50vw)] sm:px-6 sm:py-16 lg:px-8 lg:py-20"
    >
      <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-screen-2xl">
        <InquiryFormGeneralContact formUid="careers" compact removeTopMargin disableStepScroll />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</ContentLayout>
